      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's easy to say that, but it doesn't change the reality. i spent years building this, convincing everyone i was the next big thing, and now i'm just a fraud with a mountain of debt. everyone sees me as a success, but now they'll just see a loser who blew it all. there's no \"taking a step back\" from this. the damage is done and it's permanent. it feels like the only thing left is to just... disappear so the shame stops.",
